  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Hatsuyuki Sakura\" is one of the most popular works by SAGA PLANETS, a popular Japanese developer for visual novels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience Hatsuyuki Sakura for the first time in 1080p!</strong><br>This version includes the English, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, and Japanese versions. It supports Steam Achievements and Trading Cards, along with additional content. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171460/extras/43290c42ae13b47a080fb3d8503abf86.avif?t=1733997581\" width=600 height=1270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171460/extras/ee6988f377b3d6eda717813d0e9045a4.avif?t=1733997581\" width=600 height=833 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171460/extras/c9ee5e4ef657c14a6d1ba935a2bc9501.avif?t=1733997581\" width=600 height=833 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171460/extras/ccac531c5bbefa7cd86b2d5e7e6f2805.avif?t=1733997581\" width=600 height=833 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171460/extras/91305f5a5acbd7e377cef087d008442a.avif?t=1733997581\" width=600 height=833 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
